OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny evening
OL,6,Fshowers gradually dying away, leaving
OL,7,Fclearing skies, with winds falling
OL,8,Flight. This will allow temperatures to
OL,9,Fdrop with the chance of ground frost
OL,10,Fdeveloping in prone rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry, sunny and chilly start.
OL,13,FCloud bubbling up later in the morning
OL,14,Fbut still with sunny spells. Light
OL,15,Fwinds, feeling warm in the sun.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
