OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FOften
OL,6,Fcloudy on Monday with showers
OL,7,Fspreading inland from the east. Drier
OL,8,FTuesday and Wednesday with sunny
OL,9,Fspells. A strong easterly wind
OL,10,Fdeveloping, feeling cool especially on
OL,11,Fcoasts. Chilly overnight.
